{"id":615484,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/08/全球眼-你有雄兵百万，我们有人的尊严/","date":"2019-08-13T17:15:10Z","modified":"2019-08-13T17:15:10Z","title":"全球眼 | 你有雄兵百万，我们有人的尊严","content":"<p>俄罗斯人叒上街了！</p>\n<p>这一次人数有些多。8月10日，近5万俄罗斯民众聚集在莫斯科市中心，抗议几名反对派候选人被禁参加莫斯科的市议会选举。</p>\n<p>这是俄罗斯总统普京2012年连任以来，俄罗斯爆发的一场最大规模的抗议。也是俄罗斯连续第三个周末爆发的抗议活动。数千人在前两次的抗议活动中被捕。（参见：<a title=\"全球眼 | 冒着飞舞的警棍，他们又上街了\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/07/%e5%85%a8%e7%90%83%e7%9c%bc-%e5%86%92%e7%9d%80%e9%a3%9e%e8%88%9e%e7%9a%84%e8%ad%a6%e6%a3%8d%ef%bc%8c%e4%bb%96%e4%bb%ac%e5%8f%88%e4%b8%8a%e8%a1%97%e4%ba%86/\">全球眼 | 冒着飞舞的警棍，他们又上街了</a>）</p>\n<p>示威也蔓延到圣彼得堡等大城市。莫斯科的示威有245人遭到逮捕，其他声援的城市也有多人被捕。第二大城市圣彼得堡有81人被捕，包括顿河畔罗斯托夫和布扬斯克等城市也有人被捕。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/eb47e4f8-1f45-4723-acb1-6ffba990b5cf.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615485\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/eb47e4f8-1f45-4723-acb1-6ffba990b5cf.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"264\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/eb47e4f8-1f45-4723-acb1-6ffba990b5cf.jpg 680w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/eb47e4f8-1f45-4723-acb1-6ffba990b5cf-300x144.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>近年来莫斯科少见的大阵仗</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/405ccc0f-a34a-46b0-83f3-15aed47dde68.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615486\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/405ccc0f-a34a-46b0-83f3-15aed47dde68.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"592\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/405ccc0f-a34a-46b0-83f3-15aed47dde68.jpg 517w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/405ccc0f-a34a-46b0-83f3-15aed47dde68-228x300.jpg 228w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/99fb5532-9af7-4b24-a6f1-36599b55cbde.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615487\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/99fb5532-9af7-4b24-a6f1-36599b55cbde.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/99fb5532-9af7-4b24-a6f1-36599b55cbde.jpg 1060w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/99fb5532-9af7-4b24-a6f1-36599b55cbde-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/99fb5532-9af7-4b24-a6f1-36599b55cbde-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/99fb5532-9af7-4b24-a6f1-36599b55cbde-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/99fb5532-9af7-4b24-a6f1-36599b55cbde-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>有些示威者举着之前被捕的异议人士头像，还有些举着“我有选择权”的标语</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/e56f7874-0d3b-493c-ac76-77faaaa36219.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615488\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/e56f7874-0d3b-493c-ac76-77faaaa36219.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/e56f7874-0d3b-493c-ac76-77faaaa36219.jpg 680w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/e56f7874-0d3b-493c-ac76-77faaaa36219-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>公共设施戒备森严</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/d3d88786-6662-40bf-aee4-dea4fd01329e.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615489\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/d3d88786-6662-40bf-aee4-dea4fd01329e.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/d3d88786-6662-40bf-aee4-dea4fd01329e.jpg 1060w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/d3d88786-6662-40bf-aee4-dea4fd01329e-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/d3d88786-6662-40bf-aee4-dea4fd01329e-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/d3d88786-6662-40bf-aee4-dea4fd01329e-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/d3d88786-6662-40bf-aee4-dea4fd01329e-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>俄罗斯女孩奥尔加再次来到现场诵读宪法（参见：<a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAwMzMwOTA1MA==&amp;mid=2651426616&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=555609408745ae743e1cf535f3aa7207&amp;chksm=80c003adb7b78abb93f326f0b4b4988c32aa128883f158f85901676a65da0a6202bc6238f09b&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">这名风靡网络的17岁俄罗斯少女，把普京吓到了！</a>）</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/28cdf9bd-b3e8-4a36-8d9b-3d1761eb84f5.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615490\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/28cdf9bd-b3e8-4a36-8d9b-3d1761eb84f5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"402\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/28cdf9bd-b3e8-4a36-8d9b-3d1761eb84f5.jpg 965w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/28cdf9bd-b3e8-4a36-8d9b-3d1761eb84f5-300x219.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/28cdf9bd-b3e8-4a36-8d9b-3d1761eb84f5-768x562.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>乌利茨卡娅朗诵诗歌</p>\n<p>俄罗斯作家柳德米拉·乌利茨卡娅也参加了当天的集会，她在萨哈罗夫大街的舞台上，向5万抗议示威者朗诵了她的诗歌，得到满场喝彩——</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">我们有雪亮的眼，<br />\n你有军警鹰犬。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">你有雄兵百万，<br />\n我们有人的尊严。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">我们是百姓和草根，<br />\n你是克格勃官员和权贵豪门。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">你有强大的盾牌壮胆，<br />\n我们全都赤手空拳。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/b2cb5ae2-c54e-4e81-9a4a-2cc7e64749dc.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615492\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/b2cb5ae2-c54e-4e81-9a4a-2cc7e64749dc.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/b2cb5ae2-c54e-4e81-9a4a-2cc7e64749dc.jpg 1060w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/b2cb5ae2-c54e-4e81-9a4a-2cc7e64749dc-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/b2cb5ae2-c54e-4e81-9a4a-2cc7e64749dc-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/b2cb5ae2-c54e-4e81-9a4a-2cc7e64749dc-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/b2cb5ae2-c54e-4e81-9a4a-2cc7e64749dc-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_615491\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/1e518d3a-44e7-42c6-adec-d50b62d5c30f.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-615491\" class=\"wp-image-615491\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/1e518d3a-44e7-42c6-adec-d50b62d5c30f.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/1e518d3a-44e7-42c6-adec-d50b62d5c30f.jpg 1060w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/1e518d3a-44e7-42c6-adec-d50b62d5c30f-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/1e518d3a-44e7-42c6-adec-d50b62d5c30f-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/1e518d3a-44e7-42c6-adec-d50b62d5c30f-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/1e518d3a-44e7-42c6-adec-d50b62d5c30f-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-615491\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">（7月27日集会中被警察打伤的俄罗斯示威者）</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">除非你是婴孩，<br />\n否则周身何须护具覆盖？</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">我们并非来打架，只想和平地表达，<br />\n你无需逢人就抓，</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">无需挥舞拳头和棍棒，<br />\n将无辜者扔进牢房，</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/4d376c2a-c304-4dde-8d28-ce8a02330329.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615493\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/4d376c2a-c304-4dde-8d28-ce8a02330329.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/4d376c2a-c304-4dde-8d28-ce8a02330329.jpg 1060w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/4d376c2a-c304-4dde-8d28-ce8a02330329-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/4d376c2a-c304-4dde-8d28-ce8a02330329-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/4d376c2a-c304-4dde-8d28-ce8a02330329-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/4d376c2a-c304-4dde-8d28-ce8a02330329-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">把人们分化<br />\n成普通民众和警察。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">我们是百姓和草根，<br />\n你是克格勃官员和权贵豪门&#8230;&#8230;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">对我们来说，俄罗斯如此博大，<br />\n对你来说，它如同火山即将喷发。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">（诗歌翻译| Jenny）</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/fe628fdd-6e4e-410f-a9d6-e446b51e6ee7.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615494\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/fe628fdd-6e4e-410f-a9d6-e446b51e6ee7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"251\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/fe628fdd-6e4e-410f-a9d6-e446b51e6ee7.jpg 900w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/fe628fdd-6e4e-410f-a9d6-e446b51e6ee7-300x137.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/fe628fdd-6e4e-410f-a9d6-e446b51e6ee7-768x350.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>此次抗议活动并没有反对派领袖参加，如纳瓦尔尼等，因为他们基本都被拘禁。（7月28日，纳瓦尔尼被捕入狱后曾出现严重过敏症状，这种情况此前从未出现过，疑为被投毒。纳瓦尔尼在博客中表示，多年来中毒已经成为俄罗斯反对派人士的宿命，他不过是最新的案例而已。）</p>\n<p>当天抗议活动的亮点在于，不少支持自由主义的作家、博客作者、记者、歌手和明星都登台表示支持，包括音乐人切尔尼雅克、艺术家奥克西米隆、说唱歌手Face等，他们以艺术为反对普京的“投枪匕首”。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_615495\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/4addb247-8ce8-4220-88c1-380fc2449c43.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-615495\" class=\"wp-image-615495\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/4addb247-8ce8-4220-88c1-380fc2449c43.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/4addb247-8ce8-4220-88c1-380fc2449c43.jpg 1060w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/4addb247-8ce8-4220-88c1-380fc2449c43-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/4addb247-8ce8-4220-88c1-380fc2449c43-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/4addb247-8ce8-4220-88c1-380fc2449c43-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/4addb247-8ce8-4220-88c1-380fc2449c43-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-615495\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">受欢迎的博主波佩里奇尼是集会上的发言者之一</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_615496\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/27f70cc7-b69d-40d3-946b-e694e966d789.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-615496\" class=\"wp-image-615496\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/27f70cc7-b69d-40d3-946b-e694e966d789.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/27f70cc7-b69d-40d3-946b-e694e966d789.jpg 1060w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/27f70cc7-b69d-40d3-946b-e694e966d789-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/27f70cc7-b69d-40d3-946b-e694e966d789-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/27f70cc7-b69d-40d3-946b-e694e966d789-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/27f70cc7-b69d-40d3-946b-e694e966d789-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-615496\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">俄罗斯著名记者列昂尼德·帕尔菲奥诺夫说：让校长赶在警察前面惩罚他的学生，这是怎样的羞耻？</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_615497\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/08785cce-db83-4d7c-8a22-87425df92681.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-615497\" class=\"wp-image-615497\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/08785cce-db83-4d7c-8a22-87425df92681.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/08785cce-db83-4d7c-8a22-87425df92681.jpg 1060w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/08785cce-db83-4d7c-8a22-87425df92681-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/08785cce-db83-4d7c-8a22-87425df92681-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/08785cce-db83-4d7c-8a22-87425df92681-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/08785cce-db83-4d7c-8a22-87425df92681-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-615497\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">俄罗斯说唱歌手FACE （Ivan Driyomin）在台上表演</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_615498\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a7ff6f51-24e8-4273-8977-e793d7c6d5a8.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-615498\" class=\"wp-image-615498\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a7ff6f51-24e8-4273-8977-e793d7c6d5a8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a7ff6f51-24e8-4273-8977-e793d7c6d5a8.jpg 1060w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a7ff6f51-24e8-4273-8977-e793d7c6d5a8-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a7ff6f51-24e8-4273-8977-e793d7c6d5a8-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a7ff6f51-24e8-4273-8977-e793d7c6d5a8-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a7ff6f51-24e8-4273-8977-e793d7c6d5a8-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-615498\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">集会者要求释放被捕的抗议者和异议人士</p></div>\n<p>8月10日的游行规模为俄罗斯近年来所少有，但你猜猜，俄罗斯国家电视台当晚的头条新闻是什么？</p>\n<p>莫斯科有5万多抗议者要求举行公正透明的选举？不是。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a4ddec46-1330-43e3-95dd-90619e8348f1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615499\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a4ddec46-1330-43e3-95dd-90619e8348f1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"427\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a4ddec46-1330-43e3-95dd-90619e8348f1.jpg 624w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a4ddec46-1330-43e3-95dd-90619e8348f1-300x233.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>火箭试验爆炸导致5人死亡，辐射水平上升（上图）？不是。</p>\n<p>当天俄罗斯国家电视台的头条新闻是——</p>\n<p>普京出现在克里米亚的一个摩托车展上（下图）。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/334fe99e-17c5-4c97-8b7b-1f3d58840ef7.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615500\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/334fe99e-17c5-4c97-8b7b-1f3d58840ef7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"310\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/334fe99e-17c5-4c97-8b7b-1f3d58840ef7.jpg 679w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/334fe99e-17c5-4c97-8b7b-1f3d58840ef7-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>文 | Jenny （诗歌转译自俄文，原文见“阅读原文”）</p>\n","author":296,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20534],"tags":[9566,38670,14750,8584,10943,8712]}